## 9. Policy Updates
We may modify this Privacy Policy from time to time.  
Substantial changes will be announced in the support Discord or on the GitHub repository.  
Your continued use of BankerBot after changes take effect constitutes acceptance of the new policy.

---

## 10. Summary
BankerBot collects only minimal, necessary Discord data to manage its global economy functions.  
Your information is **never sold**, **shared**, or **used for advertising**.  
You remain in control of your data at all times.